rows.label: qst103310_msg001
rows.name: 犯人の侵入ルートはまだ見つかっていません(仮)

rows.label: qst103310_msg301
rows.name: 旦那さんも無念でしょう(仮)

rows.label: qst103310_msg401
rows.name: 私の力では登れません(仮)

rows.label: qst103310_msg501
rows.name: 主人と捜査を続けます(仮)

rows.label: qst103310_msg0001
rows.name:
Listen, I-I didn't...I mean, I couldn't...
I'm innocent!

rows.label: qst103310_msg0002
rows.name:
I just, I came here to clean...
And there she was...
Floating in the water...

rows.label: qst103310_msg0003
rows.name:
I pulled her out as fast
as I could, but she was
already...already...

rows.label: qst103310_msg0004
rows.name:
There were no other
visitors here.

rows.label: qst103310_msg0005
rows.name:
I'm sorry...
I only just started this job, and I...
This is all too much for me...

rows.label: qst103310_msg0006
rows.name:
I can't believe something like this
could happen here...

rows.label: qst103310_msg0007
rows.name:
I only just got this job, and
already I want to quit...
